Configuring Wi-fi Master Key
For a start, you must download and install. Launching the app, you will see that with all its versatility it has a simple intuitive and attractive interface. After the launch window opens for available connections, where you need to select the "network Analysis" to check the speed of traffic, signal strength and other characteristics of data transmission. Finally, selecting the suitable one, you connect to it without supplying a password and enjoy the connection.

Should be warned that Master Key is not related to hacking and spyware. This app is not hacking other people's passwords and did not declassify private information of users. The creators of "the Master Key" guarantees the absolute confidentiality and safety of transactions in the global web.

